08:52.797 --> 08:54.600
No, that's okay, we were just..

08:54.787 --> 08:56.120
...having a drink.

08:56.156 --> 08:58.871
I -- I just, I hadn't seen
lights on over here in ages.

08:58.906 --> 09:00.239
