around here too?

09:04.144 --> 09:06.712
Yeah! Yeah just on
the other side of the lake.

09:06.747 --> 09:08.647
Megan and I used to get into
all kinds of trouble

09:08.682 --> 09:10.348
<i>around here as kids.</i>

09:12.486 --> 09:13.718
Is that right..

09:14.814 --> 09:16.314
...Megan?

09:18.167 --> 09:20.367
Well, I should,
I should get going. Um..

09:21.028 --> 09:22.194
You guys have a great night.

09:22.229 --> 09:24.141
Yeah, have a good night, Sarah.

09:24.620 --> 09:26.153
It's really good
to see you again.

09:28.866 --> 09:30.232
See you around.

09:34.925 --> 09:36.336
I can explain.

09:38.407 --> 09:40.407
I don't even know
what to say right now.

09:43.917 --> 09:45.917
