[instrumental music]

18:34.214 --> 18:37.215
[panting]

18:39.885 --> 18:42.186
Julie! Is that you?

18:44.452 --> 18:46.553
[gasping] Hope you don't
mind me popping by.

18:46.603 --> 18:48.970
Oh, God, no, of course not.
Just a second.

18:49.996 --> 18:52.597
[breathing heavily]

18:52.756 --> 18:55.123
Let me get you some water.
Just make yourself at home.

18:55.198 --> 18:57.232
Daniel, we have company.

