19:41.481 --> 19:43.014
Yeah, and Jenny.

19:44.296 --> 19:46.312
Ah, you guys are so young.

19:46.829 --> 19:49.564
Does Jenny still have a cottage
around here too?

19:49.727 --> 19:52.190
