19:53.591 --> 19:55.680
Oh, I'm sorry.

19:56.141 --> 20:00.744
Uh, just about two weeks after
that photo was taken actually.

20:02.567 --> 20:03.667
Jesus.

20:03.703 --> 20:06.337
Quite the endurance test,
isn't it?

20:06.372 --> 20:08.859
Yeah, it's deceiving,
that's for sure.

20:08.895 --> 20:09.896
[scoffs]

20:09.932 --> 20:10.932
Yeah.

20:11.678 --> 20:13.524
I'll be right down. Sorry.

20:14.080 --> 20:15.613
Okay.

20:23.890 --> 20:25.223
- Julie, right?
- Yeah.

20:25.258 --> 20:26.691
- Daniel.
- Hi, nice to meet you.

20:26.757 --> 20:28.224
Nice to meet you.

20:28.531 --> 20:31.262
- Red or white?
- Water is good. Thank you.

20:31.297 --> 20:33.097
Sorry, I just want
to straighten this up

20:33.132 --> 20:36.500
but did, did Megan not tell you
anything about Jenny?

20:37.837 --> 20:41.505
Uh... no. Never.

20:43.343 --> 20:44.842
Why? What is it?

20:46.303 --> 20:47.437
Well..

20:48.805 --> 20:51.482
I guess it's a little bit
strange, don't you think?

20:51.517 --> 20:53.884
I mean, that was
a really big deal for us.

20:58.214 --> 21:02.249
<i>Okay. Well, I'm gonna get
another glass of wine.</i>

21:07.200 --> 21:08.852
[chuckles]

21:09.469 --> 21:12.870
So, are, are you guys up here
very long, or just the weekend?

21:12.905 --> 21:14.772
Uh, yeah, just,
just for the weekend.

21:14.807 --> 21:17.234
It's our, uh...
one year anniversary.

21:17.977 --> 21:20.211
- Oh, congratulations.
- Yeah, thanks.

21:22.548 --> 21:25.549
[instrumental music]

21:43.936 --> 21:45.936
[panting]

21:55.782 --> 21:57.515
Can you help me?

21:59.552 --> 22:01.585
Come here.

22:04.872 --> 22:06.238
Is everything okay?

22:07.090 --> 22:08.389
Yeah.

22:09.278 --> 22:11.124
You're not a good liar, Jules.

22:11.564 --> 22:14.865
You haven't said more
than a few words to me all day.

22:23.276 --> 22:25.042
Why didn't you tell me
about Jenny?

22:27.447 --> 22:29.447
Your childhood friend.

22:30.925 --> 22:34.861
Sarah, she made it sound like
you had something to do --

22:34.921 --> 22:36.352
Wait. Wait.

22:37.446 --> 22:40.447
- You saw Sarah?
- And her husband Daniel.

22:41.061 --> 22:42.093
Yeah.

22:42.702 --> 22:44.168
Yesterday.

22:46.607 --> 22:48.173
Jesus!

22:50.436 --> 22:51.769
[sighs]

22:55.007 --> 22:57.007
[exhales]

23:07.535 --> 23:10.234
Sarah, Jenny and I..

23:13.367 --> 23:16.109
...we used to swim out
into the lake.

23:17.362 --> 23:19.796
We would try to race across
to the other side.

23:20.063 --> 23:23.789
<i>[chuckles]
We were just stupid and young.</i>

23:24.416 --> 23:26.716
<i>One summer, Jenny challenged me.</i>

23:28.550 --> 23:30.774
I was about half way across..

23:34.999 --> 23:37.232
And I started cramping up,
so I..

23:38.136 --> 23:39.539
...I stopped.

23:41.535 --> 23:44.570
<i>I looked around to see
where she was..</i>

23:45.978 --> 23:49.212
...and I, I couldn't find her.

23:58.504 --> 24:00.504
[sobbing]

24:02.680 --> 24:06.368
The search and rescue pulled
her body out of the lake..

24:07.197 --> 24:08.897
...two days later.

24:10.593 --> 24:12.426
<i>And the police questioned me.</i>

24:13.565 --> 24:15.524
I was cleared of any wrongdoing.

24:22.297 --> 24:24.078
[sighs]

24:24.350 --> 24:27.125
I would never have done
anything to hurt Jenny.

24:28.234 --> 24:29.719
She was my...

24:30.885 --> 24:32.984
my best friend.

24:34.273 --> 24:35.606
[instrumental music]

24:35.891 --> 24:37.124
Hey.

24:38.187 --> 24:39.753
Hey.

24:48.463 --> 24:50.414
Do you really think that I..

24:51.133 --> 24:55.024
No, no, no. I don't know..

24:55.643 --> 24:57.242
I don't know what I thought.

24:59.978 --> 25:01.277
Come here.

25:05.905 --> 25:07.638
I guess I probably shouldn't
have invited them over

25:07.673 --> 25:09.414
for dinner on Sunday.

25:09.758 --> 25:11.695
[laughs]
No, you didn't.

25:11.743 --> 25:13.109
I did.

25:15.008 --> 25:17.114
Okay, you're cooking.

25:17.172 --> 25:18.772
- No way!
- Yeah.

25:21.400 --> 25:22.400
[grunts]

25:27.751 --> 25:30.051
I used to be really good,
you know.

25:30.087 --> 25:32.087
Like I was the only girl
on my team.

25:51.828 --> 25:53.851
God, Jackie,
this view is just --

25:53.886 --> 25:55.186
- Ahh!
- Huh!

25:55.221 --> 25:56.820
[Jules screaming]

26:25.518 --> 26:28.519
[intense music]

