Okay, okay, okay.

27:28.214 --> 27:29.180
[clears throat]

27:29.215 --> 27:31.749
[breathing heavily]

27:31.784 --> 27:33.884
[sobbing]
911?

27:33.919 --> 27:37.188
[exhales]
It's my wife, she..

27:37.338 --> 27:39.142
[sobbing]
She fell off a cliff..

27:39.191 --> 27:41.158
I don't know what happened,
she..

27:41.396 --> 27:43.396
Just wake up, babe. Please.

27:44.463 --> 27:46.464
Oh, my God,
she's not responding.

27:46.499 --> 27:47.798
She's not responding..

27:47.833 --> 27:48.899
[groans]

27:48.934 --> 27:50.868
She's not breathing..

27:50.903 --> 27:52.455
Oh, can you please save her?

27:52.505 --> 27:53.505
[laughs]

27:54.089 --> 27:55.595
Alright now.

28:08.888 --> 28:11.088
She fell off a..
She fell off a cliff.

28:11.123 --> 28:12.590
She.. Oh, my God.

28:12.625 --> 28:15.026
<i>Oh, God,
I don't know what to do.</i>

28:15.061 --> 28:17.261
What am I supposed to do?

28:17.296 --> 28:18.796
Baby, wake up.

28:20.266 --> 28:22.266
[intense music]

28:23.669 --> 28:25.338
<i>What the..</i>

28:55.668 --> 28:57.668
[gasping]

28:59.672 --> 29:01.939
[intense music]

29:02.942 --> 29:04.494
[groans]

29:14.220 --> 29:16.320
[gasping]

29:32.338 --> 29:33.338
[panting]

29:33.666 --> 29:35.166
Here we go..

29:38.778 --> 29:40.144
[inhales sharply]

29:41.180 --> 29:42.713
[groans]

29:47.419 --> 29:49.419
[coughs]

29:56.028 --> 29:57.594
[indistinct]

30:04.888 --> 30:06.521
<i>Baby, where are you?</i>

30:09.316 --> 30:10.715
<i>Are you okay?</i>

30:13.712 --> 30:16.713
[intense music]

30:19.652 --> 30:20.652
Ah!

30:22.454 --> 30:24.255
<i>Let's go home.</i>

30:24.290 --> 30:25.290
Baby!

30:26.266 --> 30:27.900
Where are you?

30:29.128 --> 30:30.594
<i>I'm so sorry.</i>

30:34.969 --> 30:36.668
I didn't mean to.

30:38.910 --> 30:40.243
Are you okay?

30:42.635 --> 30:45.202
<i>Please just call out
if you can hear me, okay?</i>

30:45.612 --> 30:46.644
<i>Baby?</i>

30:49.046 --> 30:50.612
Baby, talk to me.

30:51.851 --> 30:54.185
It was an accident I swear,
I don't know what happened..

30:54.220 --> 30:56.053
<i>I'm just, I'm freaking out.</i>

30:57.590 --> 30:58.989
I'm scared.

30:59.024 --> 31:00.090
[whimpering]

31:01.193 --> 31:02.193
[exhales]

31:03.395 --> 31:04.395
Fuck.

31:04.430 --> 31:07.431
[intense music]

31:14.804 --> 31:16.370
[crying]

31:19.645 --> 31:20.878
[breathing heavily]

31:20.983 --> 31:21.984
Baby,

31:22.988 --> 31:25.002
please just talk to me!

31:26.362 --> 31:28.329
<i>I love you so much.</i>

31:29.509 --> 31:30.813
<i>I'm scared.</i>

31:31.046 --> 31:32.245
<i>Please.</i>

31:49.920 --> 31:52.921
[sobbing]

32:00.119 --> 32:02.185
<i>Baby, please.</i>

32:03.055 --> 32:05.055
[breathing heavily]

32:07.293 --> 32:09.526
<i>Call out to me
if you can hear me, okay?</i>

32:18.137 --> 32:19.536
Hey, come on.

32:28.681 --> 32:30.047
<i>Jules, please.</i>

32:33.085 --> 32:35.752
<i>I'm so fucking scared.</i>

32:38.290 --> 32:40.324
<i>Jules, are you okay?</i>

32:44.563 --> 32:46.363
<i>Let me take you home.</i>

32:47.566 --> 32:50.567
[instrumental music]

32:55.040 --> 32:56.040
<i>Jules!</i>

32:56.787 --> 32:58.654
Where are you?

32:59.926 --> 33:01.826
I'm done playing around.

33:03.583 --> 33:05.845
<i>You must be confused.</i>

33:06.276 --> 33:08.843
I mean, why would your wife
do this to you, right?

33:11.126 --> 33:12.736
You're probably thinking..

33:12.891 --> 33:13.924
[chuckles]

33:15.752 --> 33:18.392
"Maybe she's had
a psychotic break."

33:19.131 --> 33:21.131
[instrumental music]

33:22.887 --> 33:24.188
After all...

33:25.395 --> 33:27.056
we're in love, right?

33:39.544 --> 33:41.377
I know these woods..

33:42.592 --> 33:44.959
...like the back
of my hand, Jules.

33:48.605 --> 33:50.238
I'll find you.

33:52.664 --> 33:54.097
It's only a matter of time.

33:55.534 --> 33:57.467
[thunder rumbling]

34:03.409 --> 34:04.775
[thunder rumbling]

34:04.810 --> 34:07.778
Oh, shit!

34:09.982 --> 34:11.014
[sighs]

34:20.458 --> 34:23.460
[heavy breathing]

34:33.806 --> 34:35.739
- Caw! Caw!
- Ha-ha-ha!

34:35.774 --> 34:37.841
You're so weird.

34:37.876 --> 34:40.210
- Caw!
- What is that?

34:40.245 --> 34:41.879
- What is that?
- Guess.

34:41.914 --> 34:44.514
- Obviously a rooster.
- No!

34:44.550 --> 34:46.050
[laughing]

34:46.085 --> 34:47.717
Caw! Caw!

34:47.753 --> 34:50.454
- Mm, mm, mm, mm.
- Caw! Caw!

34:50.489 --> 34:53.357
- Oh, I know. I know what it is.
- Yeah?

34:53.391 --> 34:55.359
- A seagull.
- Oh!

34:55.393 --> 34:59.696
Caw! I'm a crow.
How did you not know that?

35:02.868 --> 35:07.604
<i>Crow is the... smartest bird
in the wild.</i>

35:09.374 --> 35:11.108
[inhales sharply]

35:13.045 --> 35:16.113
[laughing]

35:18.784 --> 35:20.951
Well, I'm..

35:21.887 --> 35:23.787
...a bald eagle.

35:25.557 --> 35:27.457
Are you scared?

35:29.595 --> 35:31.394
<i>Just a little bit.</i>

35:32.397 --> 35:35.398
[crickets chirping]

35:45.644 --> 35:48.645
[dramatic music]

36:21.647 --> 36:24.648
[birds chirping]

36:35.594 --> 36:37.594
[exhales]

36:40.866 --> 36:42.866
[groans]

36:48.340 --> 36:49.673
[gasping]

36:51.977 --> 36:53.744
Don't go to sleep, Jules.

36:53.779 --> 36:55.545
<i>[thinking]
Fight it. Fight it.</i>

36:57.649 --> 36:58.982
Fight it.

36:59.017 --> 37:02.018
[retches]

37:07.859 --> 37:10.227
[groans]

37:10.262 --> 37:12.262
[breathing heavily]

37:23.775 --> 37:26.776
[groaning]

37:29.848 --> 37:31.481
[grunts]

37:34.853 --> 37:35.885
[grunts]

37:37.089 --> 37:39.556
[breathing heavily]

37:46.598 --> 37:48.331
Find the road.

37:49.201 --> 37:50.667
Find the road.

37:50.702 --> 37:52.702
[breathing heavily]

37:54.172 --> 37:56.172
[birds chirping]

38:06.618 --> 38:09.619
[breathing heavily]

38:14.626 --> 38:17.694
[Jules groaning]

38:25.003 --> 38:28.004
[bird squawking]

38:30.208 --> 38:33.209
[dramatic music]

38:38.183 --> 38:41.184
[panting]

38:48.827 --> 38:51.828
[music continues]

39:10.849 --> 39:13.850
[panting]

39:20.025 --> 39:23.026
[groaning]

39:26.198 --> 39:28.031
Okay. Phone. Phone.

39:28.066 --> 39:29.466
Phone, phone, phone, phone.

39:29.501 --> 39:30.901
Where's the phone?

39:30.936 --> 39:32.002
[mumbles]

39:32.037 --> 39:33.236
[panting]

39:33.271 --> 39:36.272
[groaning]

39:44.082 --> 39:45.549
Shit!

39:45.584 --> 39:47.384
[mumbling]

39:47.419 --> 39:49.419
[grunting]

39:50.155 --> 39:52.222
[panting]

39:52.257 --> 39:54.124
Oh, God!

39:54.159 --> 39:55.692
My phone.

39:58.497 --> 39:59.763
[grunts]

40:00.999 --> 40:02.165
Bitch!

40:02.200 --> 40:04.200
[breathing heavily]

40:07.472 --> 40:10.106
Come on. Come on.
Come on. Come on.

40:13.445 --> 40:14.644
[yells]

40:17.416 --> 40:19.416
[groans]

40:29.094 --> 40:32.095
[groaning]

40:38.403 --> 40:41.404
[breathing heavily]

40:44.676 --> 40:45.909
Bruised spleen.

40:47.012 --> 40:49.312
It's not ruptured.
It's not ruptured.

40:50.849 --> 40:51.881
Okay.

40:52.584 --> 40:54.584
[groaning]

40:58.356 --> 41:00.557
[grunting]

41:00.592 --> 41:01.992
Ankles broken.

41:02.027 --> 41:03.660
Shit!

41:04.729 --> 41:06.863
[breathing heavily]

41:06.898 --> 41:09.366
Oh, no. Okay, now.

41:09.401 --> 41:11.301
It's just a sprain.

41:11.970 --> 41:13.937
Okay. Okay.

41:13.972 --> 41:16.039
[groaning]

41:17.876 --> 41:19.976
[panting]

41:20.011 --> 41:22.979
[mumbles]

41:23.014 --> 41:25.014
[breathing heavily]

41:28.820 --> 41:30.820
[screaming]

41:33.258 --> 41:36.259
[dramatic music]

41:58.283 --> 41:59.349
[door closes]

42:28.980 --> 42:30.313
Ah!

42:50.268 --> 42:53.269
[grunting]

42:58.643 --> 43:00.810
[panting]

43:02.714 --> 43:04.113
[gunfire]

43:05.917 --> 43:07.917
[grunting]

43:09.487 --> 43:11.554
<i>Fuck off, Jackie!</i>

43:12.457 --> 43:13.457
[gunfire]

43:15.427 --> 43:16.927
Shit.

43:16.962 --> 43:19.963
[dramatic music]

43:25.370 --> 43:27.370
[breathing heavily]

43:37.649 --> 43:39.583
Why are you doing this?

43:39.618 --> 43:42.051
I just wanna talk to you, Jules.

43:44.356 --> 43:46.456
Jackie, stop!

43:50.629 --> 43:52.329
[grunting]

43:52.364 --> 43:54.998
[breathing heavily]

43:55.033 --> 43:56.232
Ah!

43:57.369 --> 44:00.337
No, no. Oh, shit! No.

44:00.372 --> 44:02.372
[whimpering]

44:06.244 --> 44:08.912
Oh, you're dead.
You're dead.

44:08.947 --> 44:13.683
Get away from me, Jackie,
you fucking psycho! Ah!

44:13.718 --> 44:16.019
[laughing]

44:16.054 --> 44:19.055
[intense music]

44:20.158 --> 44:23.159
[Jules grunting]

44:24.295 --> 44:27.296
[breathing heavily]

44:30.168 --> 44:32.635
Jackie, get away from me!

44:33.772 --> 44:36.773
[grunting]

44:39.577 --> 44:42.578
[panting]

44:43.915 --> 44:45.114
Fuck!

44:46.551 --> 44:48.217
Oh, God!

44:49.187 --> 44:50.353
No!

44:50.388 --> 44:52.389
[grunting]

44:52.424 --> 44:53.556
[thudding]

45:02.767 --> 45:04.467
Nice try!

45:05.670 --> 45:08.838
Don't you even dare, Jules.

45:08.873 --> 45:10.873
[whimpering]

45:13.078 --> 45:14.277
We'll work this out.

45:15.246 --> 45:16.512
I promise.

45:23.321 --> 45:24.754
Now, don't move.

45:27.559 --> 45:30.160
[whispering]
Why are you doing this?

45:30.195 --> 45:32.495
What, what the hell
is wrong with you?

45:32.530 --> 45:35.031
We're not doing this
right now, Jules.

45:38.403 --> 45:39.969
What the hell is wrong with you?

45:40.004 --> 45:43.106
We're not doing
this right now, Jules!

45:45.376 --> 45:47.643
Everything okay, ladies?

45:52.350 --> 45:53.649
You alright?

45:55.553 --> 45:56.653
If you say even one word

45:56.688 --> 45:58.688
I swear to God,
this won't end well.

45:58.723 --> 46:01.724
[dramatic music]

46:03.261 --> 46:04.994
Hey!

46:05.029 --> 46:07.697
You must be Daniel!

46:07.732 --> 46:09.966
<i>I've heard good things!</i>

46:10.001 --> 46:11.501
We're okay!

46:11.536 --> 46:13.403
Jules just got a bit cramped up

46:13.438 --> 46:17.540
so we're gonna, we're gonna
turn this boat back to shore!

46:17.575 --> 46:20.243
Wow, trying to make the trip
again, huh, Jules?

46:20.278 --> 46:22.312
It's impressive!

46:22.347 --> 46:24.814
<i>Alright, well, we'll see you
tomorrow night then!</i>

46:24.849 --> 46:27.350
A -- actually you know what?

46:27.385 --> 46:29.319
Tomorrow is not looking
so good for us.

46:29.354 --> 46:30.586
Tonight is!

46:31.589 --> 46:33.456
Uh, yeah.

46:33.491 --> 46:35.325
Okay, th -- that works better
actually.

46:35.360 --> 46:37.727
Uh, 8:00 p.m.

46:42.167 --> 46:44.100
Yeah, that's great!

46:46.838 --> 46:50.139
Okay, well,
uh, we'll see you then!

46:54.479 --> 46:56.345
What the fuck did I just say?

46:57.482 --> 46:58.681
You..

47:03.488 --> 47:05.822
<i>There is only one way
this works.</i>

47:05.857 --> 47:07.423
<i>You fall</i>

47:07.458 --> 47:08.925
<i>you die</i>

47:10.094 --> 47:11.394
<i>I'm in pain.</i>

47:11.429 --> 47:13.997
[Jules sobbing]

47:14.032 --> 47:15.698
<i>But of course</i>

47:15.733 --> 47:17.900
<i>it has to look like an accident.</i>

47:18.570 --> 47:20.103
[Jules whimpering]

47:20.138 --> 47:21.304
<i>How much?</i>

47:22.440 --> 47:24.607
<i>Well, you should know that,
Jules.</i>

47:24.642 --> 47:26.709
<i>You're the one
that signed the policy.</i>

47:38.389 --> 47:40.389
Did you ever love me?

47:42.360 --> 47:43.360
No.

47:47.332 --> 47:48.798
<i>I saw right through you
from the second</i>

47:48.833 --> 47:50.633
<i>I laid my eyes on you.</i>

47:50.668 --> 47:53.203
You're not gonna get away
with this.

47:53.238 --> 47:55.104
As soon as they get here

47:55.139 --> 47:58.641
I am going to scream
so goddamn loud.

47:58.676 --> 48:01.511
- No, you're not.
- Yes, I am.

48:01.546 --> 48:04.147
I'm gonna tell them exactly..

48:04.182 --> 48:06.182
[muffled scream]

48:18.463 --> 48:20.463
[coughing]

48:21.699 --> 48:23.766
[sighs]

48:23.801 --> 48:26.736
Jules? Jules?

48:26.771 --> 48:29.272
Jules, if you give
even the slightest indication

48:29.307 --> 48:31.641
that something is wrong

48:31.676 --> 48:33.676
I'm gonna take this knife
and I'm gonna stick it

48:33.711 --> 48:35.311
right into Sarah's chest.

48:35.346 --> 48:36.813
Right here.

48:36.848 --> 48:40.116
Right into her solar plexus

48:40.151 --> 48:44.287
and drag it all the way down
to her stomach

48:44.322 --> 48:46.022
before ripping it out

48:46.057 --> 48:48.624
along with everything else
that comes with it.

48:51.162 --> 48:52.728
Do you understand?

49:09.514 --> 49:11.514
[fire crackling]

49:22.126 --> 49:23.926
Your story..

49:26.464 --> 49:27.997
What your dad said..

49:31.402 --> 49:34.136
To only kill..

49:35.239 --> 49:37.239
...what keeps you alive.

49:41.412 --> 49:43.279
This isn't what he meant.

49:48.886 --> 49:51.587
You're sick, Jackie.

49:54.392 --> 49:56.492
But I can get you help.

49:59.630 --> 50:02.631
<i>[breathing heavily]</i>

50:21.919 --> 50:23.486
It's okay.

50:27.125 --> 50:29.726
It's not easy to admit.

50:29.761 --> 50:31.761
I understand.

50:37.602 --> 50:39.769
But I'll stay by your side.

50:42.407 --> 50:44.107
I will.

50:44.142 --> 50:46.042
Please, Jackie.

50:47.612 --> 50:49.445
I'll let it go.

50:50.581 --> 50:52.314
All of it.

50:54.318 --> 50:56.185
We can just get in the car
and drive

50:56.220 --> 50:58.821
and get as far away
from this place as possible..

50:59.524 --> 51:01.390
...before they show up.

51:02.126 --> 51:03.325
Please.

51:06.230 --> 51:09.331
I never told you
about my first wife, did I?

51:11.402 --> 51:12.601
Erica.

51:14.839 --> 51:17.106
We got married
when I was only 19.

51:18.443 --> 51:20.910
I guess it slipped my mind
until now.

51:23.748 --> 51:26.749
[dramatic music]

51:37.662 --> 51:39.028
[groaning]

51:47.004 --> 51:48.304
How?

51:51.509 --> 51:53.642
We were on vacation.

51:55.179 --> 51:56.579
She went swimming

51:56.614 --> 51:58.848
after having a few too many.

52:00.051 --> 52:01.617
I mourned her.

52:03.354 --> 52:04.954
Prayed with her parents.

52:05.623 --> 52:07.256
Read at her funeral.

52:10.828 --> 52:12.661
I'll do the same at yours.

52:17.135 --> 52:19.235
I know what you're trying to do,
Jules.

52:20.538 --> 52:23.038
And this little game
that you're playing right now..

52:24.876 --> 52:26.175
...won't work.

52:28.980 --> 52:31.347
How much was she worth?

52:32.783 --> 52:35.784
[inhales]

52:36.888 --> 52:38.721
She was priceless.

52:43.861 --> 52:46.696
I never thought I would be
having dinner with Megan again.

52:46.731 --> 52:47.964
Just breathe, baby

52:47.999 --> 52:49.665
and just be nice.

52:49.700 --> 52:51.200
It'll be over
before you know it.

52:51.235 --> 52:52.602
Yeah, that's easy
for you to say.

52:52.637 --> 52:53.702
Um..

52:54.572 --> 52:56.205
- Hi!
- Hey!

52:56.240 --> 52:57.707
So glad you guys could make it!

52:57.742 --> 52:59.142
- <i>Yeah! Thank you!</i>
- Come in, come in.

52:59.177 --> 53:01.043
Don't worry about your shoes,
just make yourself at home.

53:01.078 --> 53:04.080
Wow! Megan,
it is crazy to be back here.

53:04.115 --> 53:05.314
- It's like a time capsule.
- Yeah.

53:05.349 --> 53:06.749
It's been a,
it's been a while for you.

53:06.784 --> 53:08.017
- That's for sure.
- Yeah.

53:08.052 --> 53:09.385
We brought a nice bottle
of wine.

53:09.420 --> 53:10.586
Oh, great!
Uh, yeah, follow me.

53:10.621 --> 53:11.654
The glasses
are in the kitchen here.

53:11.689 --> 53:13.556
Great! Open up
a nice bottle of wine.

53:13.591 --> 53:15.658
<i>Yes, let's.</i>

53:16.994 --> 53:18.828
- Thanks.
- <i>Jules!</i>

53:18.863 --> 53:20.696
Oh, it's so nice
to see you again.

53:24.035 --> 53:25.201
Are you okay?

53:25.236 --> 53:27.102
Yeah, I -- I'm fine.

53:28.539 --> 53:31.941
Did you, uh, strain yourself
with all the paddling, Jules?

53:34.278 --> 53:35.744
Yeah, that's it.

53:36.647 --> 53:38.181
Nothing, a few painkillers

53:38.216 --> 53:39.582
and a shot of whiskey
won't cure.

53:39.617 --> 53:41.117
Well, I hear that!

53:41.152 --> 53:43.653
<i>Well, we, well,
we brought a bottle of wine</i>

53:43.688 --> 53:45.488
<i>would you like to come
have a glass?</i>

53:45.523 --> 53:46.789
Love to.

53:52.697 --> 53:54.797
[instrumental music]

53:54.832 --> 53:56.732
[exhales]

53:56.767 --> 53:59.302
[indistinct chatter]

53:59.337 --> 54:02.204
<i>So, Jules,
when did you know about Megan?</i>

54:04.275 --> 54:06.575
<i>Julie? Julie?</i>

54:07.511 --> 54:09.679
Sorry, I -- I missed that.

54:09.714 --> 54:11.080
<i>Just..</i>

54:11.115 --> 54:13.115
I was asking when do you knew

54:13.150 --> 54:14.850
Megan was the one?

54:17.588 --> 54:19.788
Megan, uh..

54:21.025 --> 54:23.092
I don't know.

54:23.127 --> 54:25.728
Well, what I -- I think
she means to say

54:25.763 --> 54:27.162
is that..

